(53, 'How do I choose the right franchise for me?', 'You can explore franchise opportunities by visiting the 1851 Franchise website and browsing through their extensive directory of franchise brands. You can filter opportunities based on industry, investment range, and other criteria to find the best match for your interests and goals.', '2025-01-23 11:26:14.112604', '2025-01-27 11:41:07.372702', 179, 179, '2025-01-27 11:41:07.372702'),
